      "action_code": "H8A000",
      "references": [],
      "text": "The previous question on the motion to recommit was ordered pursuant to clause 2(b) of rule XIX.",
      "type": "action"
    },
    {
      "acted_at": "2026-04-15T15:37:45-04:00",
      "action_code": "H8D000",
      "references": [],
      "text": "POSTPONED PROCEEDINGS - At the conclusion of debate on H.R. 6398, the Chair put the question on motion to recommit, and by voice vote, announced that the noes had prevailed. Mrs. Grijalva demanded the yeas and nays and the Chair postponed further proceedings until a time to be announced.",
